sequenceDiagram
  %% Authored stress fixture (Mermaid@11.12.2): many participants + mixed types to stress horizontal spacing.

  participant U as User
  participant WEB as Web
  participant API@{ "type" : "control" }
  participant AUTH@{ "type" : "entity" }
  participant Q@{ "type" : "queue" }
  participant W@{ "type" : "boundary" }
  participant DB@{ "type" : "database" }
  participant LOG@{ "type" : "collections" }

  U->>WEB: open
  WEB->>API: request
  API->>AUTH: verify
  AUTH-->>API: ok
  API->>Q: enqueue
  Q->>W: deliver
  W->>DB: write
  DB-->>W: ok
  W->>LOG: record
  LOG-->>W: ok
  API-->>WEB: 200
  WEB-->>U: done
